y want you to believe this happened in the LA Mayors race\u2026\n\n3rd place jumps to 1st in *every* ballot drop *after* Election Day\n\nDefies all mathematical probability, the law of averages and has never happened in US election history\n\nNo one with a functional brain believes this", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 3591}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsnGjVJf", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 15, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8666827, "raw_content": "It just shifts the work load and costs to the consumer.\n\nInstead of having one good expert at a company, each of the consumers have to do more and more of the workload.\n\nI remember in the olden days you could go into a hardware store ---- and blindfold one of the employees ----- ask them where something is and they could walk to it is 20 seconds. People had a purpose back then.", "author": "cyberrigger", "created": 1780905871241, "profile_picture": "0UVsiKsLavnh", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "cyberrigger", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Here is my conclusion on AI and Jeets ----> it does not reduce the workload and cost", "last_comment_created": 1780908145132, "content": "<p>It just shifts the work load and costs to the consumer.</p>\n<p>Instead of having one good expert at a company, each of the consumers have to do more and more of the workload.</p>\n<p>I remember in the olden days you could go into a hardware store ---- and blindfold one of the employees ----- ask them where something is and they could walk to it is 20 seconds. People had a purpose back then.</p>\n", "score_